Title: Nest Of Bloodsuckers
Descriptions: Can you believe it? One of our hunting parties found a nesting ground of Bloodsuckers deep in the woods South of Stary Yar... There is a cash reward if you can deal with them and eliminate the Bloodsucker queen
Find a nest deep in the woods South of Stary Yar and kill as many Bloodsuckers as you can. Eliminate the Bloodsucker queen for a bonus.
Nice work! Hopefully thats the last of those fuckers, here is your payment.
ObjectiveText: Find the Bloodsucker nest and kill as many as possible. Kill a Bloodsucker queen for added bonus. Don't forget to gather the skins from the big ones and sell them.
